ca.cwfgm.psaas.api.frontier

Class UnitSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.cwfgm.psaas.api.frontier.UnitSettings

  • public abstract class UnitSettings
extends Object
    Settings that define which units will be used when data is exported in summary or statistics files. All units are optional with application defaults being used for anything that isn't specified.
